:"84bcd144932bb5ab10a7e3cc8f40ae19d1ca0be6","tid":137073,"uid":2059,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-27T19:03:59.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n突然好似咩都自己一個面對咁<br />\n好想有人一直陪住我"},{"pid":"c4045446d77ba2669c455488a75caeb32c042b2a","tid":137073,"uid":62996,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-27T19:05:46.000Z","msg":"呢兩個月都係咁<br />\n上星期返返下工忍唔住冇啦啦喊左<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"a6c0901b296f2efa82c2236ab2c7421eeb6de4b5","tid":137073,"uid":35193,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-27T19:14:52.000Z","msg":"2017年之後到2月中旬無一日過得好<br />\n發生得太多事<br />\n2月中果陣連笑都笑唔出<br />\n甚至仲諗過想死<br />\n好彩上個禮拜生日嘅前幾日<br />\n啲老師朋友同學都好關心我<br />\n如果唔係真係諗住生日果日死咗去<br />\n雖然搵得翻笑嘅理由<br />\n但係個心真係好攰<br />\n已經無動力做人<br />\n連喊都喊唔出"},{"pid":"ccfb4ba3be8f05ae1f453581a24fe90469c4c51f","tid":137073,"uid":25044,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-27T19:17:45.000Z","msg":"唉做人真係好撚灰"},{"pid":"c6395c713cbd03c2625ba0a4ddac7f7326ddb0f3","tid":137073,"uid":50325,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-27T19:23:21.000Z","msg":"今日連midterm都唔返"},{"pid":"010a624b9ea88327cd3c3e5c76ee78260e9b1552","tid":137073,"uid":31368,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-27T19:27:53.000Z","msg":"係咪天氣問題<br />\n利申<br />\n屋企翻天覆地"},{"pid":"dc2b6575129574ad2e09e9abb0fbf36c1fde4231","tid":137073,"uid":25044,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-27T19:33:02.000Z","msg":"又喊啦痴線架"},{"pid":"02710b41334b9ea62ab74eef4430ec483b395c1e","tid":137073,"uid":15186,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-27T19:39:10.000Z","msg":"same <br />\n同條女炒左2次1個星期内<br />\n平日真係一年都鬧唔到一次"},{"pid":"b2d068aab0826974e80b1a1a76ec81db2191bdc4","tid":137073,"uid":76951,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-27T19:59:57.000Z","msg":"我呀<img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/bye.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n好想有人關心，好想有人錫<br />\n好想有人分擔，好想有人陪我聽歌<br />\n好想有人帶領我走出陰霾<br />\n一齊簡簡單單開開心心快快樂樂咁生活<img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"05fdf334d039f68c08a3a88b52c490f80acc3eff","tid":137073,"uid":60864,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-27T23:08:57.000Z","msg":"唔夠瞓嗰陣 亂諗野嘅情況更加嚴重<img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n救命<br />\n對前途嘅迷茫 <br />\n唔甘心  但係又冇勇氣去改變<br />\n呢個唔三唔四嘅狀態真無好討厭<br />\n仲有出到嚟社會發現自己抗逆力咁差 少少事就畀人打沉<br />\n有冇人可以呃下我 呢個階段好快可以過去<br />\n我睇唔到前路 覺得前路只會一直差落去<img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/biggrin.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"7ab26ed31eabb1db053b753eb8ba680d66a67d50","tid":137073,"uid":60864,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-27T23:09:36.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>唔夠瞓嗰陣 亂諗野嘅情況更加嚴重<img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n救命<br />\n對前途嘅迷茫 <br />\n唔甘心  但係又冇勇氣去改變<br />\n呢個唔三唔四嘅狀態真無好討厭<br />\n仲有出到嚟社會發現自己抗逆力咁差 <span style=\"color: red;\">小小</span>事就畀人打沉<br />\n有冇人可以呃下我 呢個階段好快可以過去<br />\n我睇唔到前路 覺得前路只會一直差落去<img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/biggrin.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote>"},{"pid":"874ebce4f5ae4bc13eba168bc77778340b723447","tid":137073,"uid":73805,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-27T23:39:16.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote>唔夠瞓嗰陣 亂諗野嘅情況更加嚴重<img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n救命<br />\n對前途嘅迷茫 <br />\n唔甘心  但係又冇勇氣去改變<br />\n呢個唔三唔四嘅狀態真無好討厭<br />\n仲有出到嚟社會發現自己抗逆力咁差 <span style=\"color: red;\">小小</span>事就畀人打沉<br />\n有冇人可以呃下我 呢個階段好快可以過去<br />\n我睇唔到前路 覺得前路只會一直差落去<img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/biggrin.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote></blockquote><br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/bye.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n前路只會繼續差落去係事實黎 我相信同在乎既事情喺香港通通都冇價值 喺個黑洞到掙扎極都見唔到光<br />\n講到尾都係自己垃撚圾到又連自我麻醉都做唔到<img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"e126c4ee0283aa371613bc3978ab523ab6049167","tid":137073,"uid":88048,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-28T03:10:15.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>唔夠瞓嗰陣 亂諗野嘅情況更加嚴重<img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n救命<br />\n對前途嘅迷茫 <br />\n唔甘心  但係又冇勇氣去改變<br />\n呢個唔三唔四嘅狀態真無好討厭<br />\n仲有出到嚟社會發現自己抗逆力咁差 少少事就畀人打沉<br />\n有冇人可以呃下我 呢個階段好快可以過去<br />\n我睇唔到前路 覺得前路只會一直差落去<img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/biggrin.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n逼自己盡量早訓係會好少少既，起碼個身體無咁累先<img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"22d5343c2d7634da6ba261193b1298d93751b54c","tid":137073,"uid":3517,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-28T03:31:29.000Z","msg":"同你一樣<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n1月既時候日日都過得好開心, 一去到2月就好似跌左落谷底咁<br />\n同啲朋友傾過但都情緒仲係好低落<img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"9661612b93474736ed4a08c517aca0a16d4e8930","tid":137073,"uid":59641,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-28T03:38:42.000Z","msg":"呢幾日都特別易發嬲<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"03f85ab0abe9c120fbc030a045cc9b5bfb4ca924","tid":137073,"uid":24328,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-28T05:07:10.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>我呀<img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/bye.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n好想有人關心，好想有人錫<br />\n好想有人分擔，好想有人陪我聽歌<br />\n好想有人帶領我走出陰霾<br />\n一齊簡簡單單開開心心快快樂樂咁生活<img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<br />\nMe 2<br />\n點解冇人明白我<br />\n我淨係想靜靜地有人陪下我"}]}